title: Baked beef spaghetti
ingredients: ['340g spaghetti', '160g chopped onions', '150g chopped green peppers', '450g lean minced beef', '450g tinned chopped tomatoes', '1/2 (300g) tin chopped mushrooms, drained', '1 teaspoon dried oregano', '225g grated mild Cheddar cheese, divided', '1 (295g) tin condensed cream of mushroom soup', '4 tablespoons water', '4 tablespoons grated Parmesan cheese']
